probes/p_eqH.spthy -- user fst(<x, y>)=x before builtin fst(<x.1, x.2>)=x.1: var compare = name then index
probes/p_eqI.spthy -- <x, zz> before <x, b, c>: tuples compare as RIGHT-NESTED binary pair apps, not flattened lists
probes/p_pw1.spthy -- wide-tuple wrap shapes wfa-wfd: elements fill at col('<')+1; '<' alone when first elem one-liner cannot sit beside it; '>' beside last elem unless that elem is multi-line (then own line at col('<')); same in lhs argument position
